  <summary date="2020-04-02T13:54:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Conflicts from Political Fundraising Act of 2019

This bill requires presidentially appointed executive branch officials to disclose whether they have solicited donations for or contributed funds to political action committees, political non-profits, or industry trade associations.</summary>
